Package civitas.celestis.math.vector

Interface Vector<N extends Number,V extends Vector<N,V>>

Type Parameters:
N - The type of number this vector uses
V - Itself (the parameter and result of various operations)
All Superinterfaces:
Collectable<N>, Group<N>, Listable<N>, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
BigVector<N,V>, DecimalVector<V>, DoubleVector<V>, FloatVector<V>, IntegerVector<V>, IntVector<V,F>, LongVector<V,D>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Complex, Decimal2, Decimal3, Decimal4, DecimalQuaternion, Double2, Double3, Double4, Float2, Float3, Float4, FloatQuaternion, Int2, Int3, Int4, Integer2, Integer3, Integer4, LinearColor, Long2, Long3, Long4, Quaternion
public interface Vector<N extends Number,V extends Vector<N,V>> extends Group<N>, Serializable
A mathematical tuple of numbers.

      @Nonnull V min(@Nonnull V v)
